opscc_deg = readRDS(file = params$input_data["opscc_deg"])
hmsc_deg = read.table(file =  params$input_data["hmsc_deg"],row.names = 1,sep = ",",header = T)

hmsc_top = hmsc_deg %>% filter(avg_log2FC > log2(volcano_fc) &
                                 fdr < volcano_fdr) %>% rownames()
opscc_top = opscc_deg %>% filter(avg_log2FC > log2(volcano_fc) &
                                   fdr < volcano_fdr) %>% rownames()

print ("intersect genes:")
## [1] "intersect genes:"
intersected_genes = intersect(hmsc_top,opscc_top)
intersected_genes
## [1] "PTN"    "CENPW"  "UBE2T"  "C9orf3" "PTRF"
plt = volcano_plot(
  de_genes = opscc_deg,
  fc_cutoff = 1.1,
  fdr_cutoff = volcano_fdr,
  ident1 = "HPV33 positive",
  ident2 = "HPV33 negative",
  top_genes_text = 0,
  show_gene_names = intersected_genes
  ) +
  ggtitle("Differential Gene Expression by HPV Status")  + 
  expand_limits(y = c(0, 4))+
  coord_cartesian(clip = "off")

plt
